title: slimefun报错求解
author: 殇蚀烬月
txt_content:
加载了第一个世界显示信息[09:46:47] [Server thread/INFO]: [远古工艺] 正在加载世界中的方块 "world"
[09:46:47] [Server thread/INFO]: [远古工艺] 可能需要花费一些时间...
[09:46:47] [Server thread/INFO]: [远古工艺] 加载方块中... 100% (已完成 - 13ms)
[09:46:47] [Server thread/INFO]: [远古工艺] 共计加载 224 个方块，位于世界 "world"
[09:46:47] [Server thread/INFO]: [远古工艺] Avg: 0.058ms/方块复制代码
以后就会报如下错误
[09:46:47] [Server thread/WARN]: [Slimefun] Task #164 for Slimefun v4.1.15 generated an exception
java.lang.NullPointerException: null
        at me.mrCookieSlime.Slimefun.api.BlockStorage.<init>(BlockStorage.java:174) ~[?:?]
        at me.mrCookieSlime.Slimefun.SlimefunStartup.lambda$onEnable$0(SlimefunStartup.java:283) ~[?:?]
        at org.bukkit.craftbukkit.v1_12_R1.scheduler.CraftTask.run(CraftTask.java:63) ~[Paper-1.12.2.jar:git-Paper-1604]
        at org.bukkit.craftbukkit.v1_12_R1.scheduler.CraftScheduler.mainThreadHeartbeat(CraftScheduler.java:423) ~[Paper-1.12.2.jar:git-Paper-1604]
        at net.minecraft.server.v1_12_R1.MinecraftServer.D(MinecraftServer.java:840) ~[Paper-1.12.2.jar:git-Paper-1604]
        at net.minecraft.server.v1_12_R1.DedicatedServer.D(DedicatedServer.java:423) ~[Paper-1.12.2.jar:git-Paper-1604]
        at net.minecraft.server.v1_12_R1.MinecraftServer.C(MinecraftServer.java:774) ~[Paper-1.12.2.jar:git-Paper-1604]
        at net.minecraft.server.v1_12_R1.MinecraftServer.run(MinecraftServer.java:666) ~[Paper-1.12.2.jar:git-Paper-1604]
        at java.lang.Thread.run(Thread.java:748) [?:1.8.0_242]复制代码导致除了world这一个世界以外所有的世界方块均无法加载，尝试了升级前置，更换版本，删除世界数据几种方法都没解决

请问有大佬知道怎么解决吗，困扰我很长一段时间了
